OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for at least 26
OL,7,Fyears for murdering his ex-wife and
OL,8,Fburying her in his back garden.
OL,10,FAlireza Askari, 42, admitted killing
OL,11,FParia Veisi, 37, at the property they
OL,12,Fhad previously shared in Penylan,
OL,13,FCardiff, in April last year.
OL,15,FCardiff Crown Court heard Ms Veisi had
OL,16,Frecently separated from her husband
OL,17,Fand moved out of the house earlier
OL,18,Fthat month.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FIt was in the garden of the property
OL,7,Fthat police found her body, buried in
OL,8,Fa "makeshift grave" concealed by patio
OL,9,Fslabs, soil and newly-planted flowers.
OL,11,FOn Friday, Mrs Justice Stacey
OL,12,Fsentenced Askari to life imprisonment
OL,13,Fwith a minimum term of 26 years for
OL,14,Fthe "cold-blooded murder" of Ms Veisi.
OL,16,FWilliam Hughes KC, prosecuting, said
OL,17,FAskari had murdered his ex-wife in the
OL,18,Fconservatory of the address, before
OL,19,Fattempting to destroy any evidence
OL,20,Fwith the assistance of his aunt,
OL,21,FMaryam Delavary.
OL,26,@pD@COUpD@SO]vD@EOUvD@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FThe court previously heard Askari and
OL,7,FMs Veisi moved to the UK from Iran in
OL,8,F2010 and had married, but were living
OL,9,Fseparately at the time of the murder.
OL,11,FAnalysis of Askari's phone found he
OL,12,Fhad been texting a woman in Iran,
OL,13,Fbelieved to be his girlfriend, prior
OL,14,Fto the killing.
OL,16,FIn one message, he told the woman:
OL,17,F"I'm planning for them to kill her in
OL,18,FIran."
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@FO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FOn the day of the attack, Askari
OL,7,Fpurchased the suspected murder weapon,
OL,8,Fa set of kitchen knives, from a
OL,9,Fsupermarket before returning home.
OL,11,FMr Hughes said: "It is the prosecution
OL,12,Fcase that the first defendant, Alireza
OL,13,FAskari, murdered Paria Veisi at around
OL,14,F4.30pm on April 12 in the conservatory
OL,15,Fof his home address.
OL,17,F"After Alireza Askari had murdered
OL,18,FParia Veisi, he prevented the lawful
OL,19,Fburial of her body by placing her
OL,20,Fremains in a makeshift grave in the
OL,21,Fgarden."
OL,26,@sD@QOUyD@AOU}D@HO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FLater that afternoon, Askari rang
OL,7,FDelavary, his aunt, who travelled from
OL,8,FLondon to Cardiff in a taxi, before
OL,9,Fmaking another trip to the
OL,10,Fsupermarket, where he purchased
OL,11,Fbleach, compost and plants.
OL,13,FMr Hughes said: "The prosecution case
OL,14,Fis that, on arrival, Maryam Delavary
OL,15,Fwas to assist in the covering up of
OL,16,FParia's murder."
OL,26,@uD@QOUxD@PO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
