PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FA friend of Ms Veisi contacted South
OL,7,FWales Police the day after the murder,
OL,8,Fraising concerns that she was "being
OL,9,Fkept against her will by her ex-
OL,10,Fhusband" and a missing person
OL,11,Finvestigation was subsequently
OL,12,Flaunched.
OL,14,FOn April 15, Askari was arrested while
OL,15,Fdriving back to Cardiff from
OL,16,FBirmingham and canisters containing
OL,17,Fcaustic soda were found inside the
OL,18,Fvehicle.
OL,26,@pD@_OUrD@HO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
