OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FMr Hughes said: "These chemicals, say
OL,7,Fthe prosecution, were to be used in
OL,8,Fthe destruction of Paria's remains."
OL,10,FFollowing a search of the property, Ms
OL,11,FVeisi's body was found in the rear
OL,12,Fgarden beneath patio slabs, soil and
OL,13,Fnewly-planted flowers.
OL,15,FShe had suffered four stab wounds,
OL,16,Fwith injuries to her chest and neck.
OL,26,@nD@QOUpD@dO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/14
