PN,46808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FAddressing Askari, Mrs Justice Stacey
OL,7,Fsaid: "She was in the prime of her
OL,8,Flife, her death has destroyed her
OL,9,Ffamily's happiness, as you knew it
OL,10,Fwould.
OL,12,F"You subjected Paria to abuse at home
OL,13,Fand (she) was fearful of you, Paria
OL,14,Fconfided to her friends how scared she
OL,15,Fwas of you.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,F"You recruited your aunt, the second
OL,7,Fdefendant, immediately... You did
OL,8,Feverything in your power to cover up
OL,9,Fthe murder, to destroy evidence and to
OL,10,Fhinder the South Wales Police
OL,11,Finvestigation.
OL,13,F"You killed your ex-wife because she
OL,14,Fwanted a divorce and had left you less
OL,15,Fthan two weeks earlier.
OL,17,F"Your hypocrisy was staggering ` at
OL,18,Fthe same time you wanted (Paria) out
OL,19,Fof the way so you could take up with
OL,20,Fyour girlfriend in Iran."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU|D@YO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/14
