PN,46810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FAskari, of Penylan, Cardiff,
OL,7,Fpreviously pleaded guilty to murder
OL,8,Fand preventing the lawful and decent
OL,9,Fburial of a body at Cardiff Crown
OL,10,FCourt.
OL,12,FA further charge of assault
OL,13,Foccasioning actual bodily harm was
OL,14,Fordered to lie on file.
OL,16,FDelavary, 48, of Australia Road, White
OL,17,FCity Estate, west London, previously
OL,18,Fpleaded guilty to perverting the
OL,19,Fcourse of justice.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FShe was sentenced to five years and
OL,7,Fsix months imprisonment.
OL,9,FFollowing the sentencing, Paria's
OL,10,Fsister, Heliya Veysi, said: "Today's
OL,11,Fverdict will never bring Paria back to
OL,12,Fus, nor can it heal the deep and
OL,13,Flasting pain of her loss. However, it
OL,14,Fis an important step toward justice
OL,15,Fand accountability.
OL,26,@rD@]OU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,F"Our family sincerely thanks South
OL,7,FWales Police, the judicial system and
OL,8,Fall those who, with dedication,
OL,9,Fresponsibility and persistent effort,
OL,10,Fplayed a role in ensuring that justice
OL,11,Fwas served.
OL,13,F"Paria was not just a victim, she was
OL,14,Fa beloved daughter, sister and friend,
OL,15,Fwho was kind, full of life and deeply
OL,16,Floved. Her memory will forever remain
OL,17,Fin our hearts and the pain of losing
OL,18,Fher is a wound that time will never
OL,19,Ffully heal."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G12/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46813
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,FMeanwhile Detective Chief Inspector
OL,7,FMatt Powell from South Wales Police
OL,8,Fhas recognised the bravery shown by
OL,9,FParia's family.
OL,11,F"They have been deprived of many happy
OL,12,Fyears with Paria, and our thoughts
OL,13,Fcontinue to be them.
OL,15,F"It has become clear throughout this
OL,16,Finvestigation that Paria was a much-
OL,17,Floved lady, popular with all those who
OL,18,Fknew her, including those who had
OL,19,Ftheir hair cut by her. She will be
OL,20,Fsorely missed by everyone.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G13/14
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46814
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1773667692
OL,3,CMan jailed after killing ex-wife and
OL,4,Cburying her in garden
OL,6,F"Now Alireza Askari and Maryam
OL,7,FDelavary will spend a long time in
OL,8,Fprison for their crimes. Whilst
OL,9,FParia's family and friends can never
OL,10,Fget her back, I hope they take some
OL,11,Fcomfort from knowing that justice has
OL,12,Fbeen done.
OL,14,F"I would finally like to thank all the
OL,15,Fwitnesses in this case, and the
OL,16,Fcommunity for the support and
OL,17,Funderstanding they gave throughout our
OL,18,Finvestigation, especially in the early
OL,19,Fstages when so much focus was on the
OL,20,FPenylan area of Cardiff where this
OL,21,Fhorrific murder took place."
OL,26,@}D@\O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G14/14
